{
  "stem": "24364.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I-- that was very unpleasant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "That had never happened to me before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We-- the boat, we were about three weeks I believe in Tulcea before we sailed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I have no idea why we stood there so long.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But then we sailed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we got to Istanbul, where we anchored for a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And actually, the Jews in Istanbul were very nice and they sent us some food, some bread, and-- and I think some-- some other stuff.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I think we stood there for a day or two and then we continued.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And then we got to Crete, eventually.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And we stopped there in Heraklion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And unfortunately, it was on the eve of the breakout of the war between Italy and Greece.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And so we were stuck again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we stood on Crete for about three weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And during that time, the crew, who really consisted of not very honorable people, decided that it was not a good idea to sail during the time of war.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they burned part of our precious coal and threw the other part into the ocean and the captain refused to sail.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the-- our-- we had a group which was called the Haganah, which consisted of young men who tried to keep order on the boat.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so they took over and they manned the ship.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they put the cabin-- locked the captain into a cabin and they took over the ship.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they worked as engineers and stokers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was decided at that time that Palestine was too far, so they would go to Cyprus, because we didn't have enough coal.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
